msgid ""
"Note from the devs:\n"
"Congratulations for getting this far in the Paper Lily story!\n"
"Thank you so much for your support and enthusiasm for this little world we created. Please don't hesitate to leave a review if you have the time, it helps immensely.\n"
"\n"
"We're still only two idiots making this game, so if you want to support future development please consider purchasing the supporter pack!"
msgstr ""
"開發者的訊息：\n"
"恭喜你到達了這個階段的 Paper Lily 故事！\n"
"非常感謝你對我們創造的這個小小世界的支持與熱情。如果有時間的話，請不要吝於留下評論，這對我們幫助很大。\n"
"\n"
"我們仍然只是兩個在製作這個遊戲的笨蛋，所以如果你想要支持未來的開發的話請考慮購買支持者包！"

